text: Attack of the Lederhosen Zombies is a 2016 Austrian horror comedy movie directed by Dominik Hartl and starring Laurie Calvert, Gabriela Marcinková, Oscar Dyekjær Giese, Margarete Tiesel, Karl Fischer, Kari Rakkola. ==Other websites== * Category:2016 comedy movies Category:2016 horror movies Category:Austrian comedy movies Category:Austrian horror movies Category:Movies set in the Alps
title: Attack of the Lederhosen Zombies
